@startuml Sequence Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

actor User1
participant "Client1\n(HiddenChat)" as Client1
participant "Server\n(Socket.IO)" as Server
participant "Client2\n(HiddenChat)" as Client2
participant "Steganography" as Stego
participant "Crypto" as Crypto
participant "DB" as DB

== Sending Message ==
User1 -> Client1: Type message & select image
Client1 -> Crypto: encryptMessage(text, key)
Crypto --> Client1: encrypted text
Client1 -> Stego: encodeMessageIntoImage(image, encrypted)
Stego --> Client1: encoded image (base64)
Client1 -> Server: send_message(room, encodedImage, sender)
Client1 -> DB: add(message)
DB --> Client1: saved

== Receiving Message ==
Server -> Client2: receive_message(encodedImage, sender)
Client2 -> Stego: decodeMessageFromImage(encodedImage)
Stego --> Client2: encrypted text
Client2 -> Crypto: decryptMessage(encrypted, key)
Crypto --> Client2: decrypted text
Client2 -> Client2: Play sound & display message
Client2 -> DB: add(message)
DB --> Client2: saved

note right Client2
    If decryption fails,
    show as plain image
end note
@enduml
